The paper deals with the problem of tracking control for unknown Euler-Lagrange systems using Gaussian Process regression. This involves machine learning techniques and control theory, which are relevant to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
